name: Anthony GEORGE et al. v. OAKHURST REALTY, INC., et al.

parties: Anthony GEORGE et al. v. OAKHURST REALTY, INC., et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The motion of defendant Oakhurst Realty, Inc. to remand this case to the Superior Court for hearing on the merits as prayed is denied.

attorneys: Adolph N. Anderson, Jr., Providence, for plaintiffs.
John H. Hines, Jr., Providence, for Oak-hurst Realty, Inc. Selya & Iannuccillo, Inc., Martin L. Greenwald, Providence, for Downing Associates, Inc.
